    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? i mean i know it sounds scary but i've been feeling super drained all day. like my whole body just feels heavy. don't you think it's more likely just dehydration or maybe just a pinched nerve from sitting in that cramped economy seat for 12 hours? i'm pretty sure if i just sleep it off i'll be fine in the morning. you're sure i need a hospital for this?",
