    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just really hesitant about going to a hospital in japan when i dont speak the language well and it's so expensive... i was reading online that sometimes these things are just \"transient\" and pass on their own if you just relax. if i take some aspirin and try to stretch it out, would that be okay to wait a few hours? i really just want to sleep it off first.",
